stimulus:
Help rate the audio stimuli!

Make sure you can hear audio!

In each trial you will hear one syllable.

After you have heard the syllable, please indicate the identity of the perceived syllable,i.e., which syllable you think you heard,

You will then hear the syllable again once.

Then, please indicate how prototypical is the syllable of the pereived identity on a scale from 1 to 7

Press any key to begin.
